Index is the position of character in the given String
The index always starts 0
Every character has an index including special charcater and spaces !@#$

(*) Method
Methods are behaviors / actions done to objects
Strings are something callled objects

Most important part of methods are what it takes and what it retuns 

Argument is the information that the method takes

